  "text": "All five core document-model files were located by glob and confirmed with grep for their class declarations: (1) `include/sfx2/objsh.hxx` defines `SfxObjectShell` \u2014 the base document shell class for all document types. (2) `sw/inc/doc.hxx` defines `class SwDoc final` \u2014 the Writer document model. (3) `sc/inc/document.hxx` defines `class ScDocument` \u2014 the Calc spreadsheet document model. (4) `sd/inc/drawdoc.hxx` defines `class SdDrawDocument final : public FmFormModel` \u2014 the Impress/Draw document. (5) `include/sfx2/app.hxx` defines `class SfxApplication final : public SfxShell` \u2014 the application framework entry point. The dependency chain flows from SfxApplication (top-level app) \u2192 SfxObjectShell (base document shell) \u2192 concrete document classes (SwDoc, ScDocument, SdDrawDocument).",
